---
title: One-Pot Tortilla Soup with Meatless Farm® Protein, Black Beans and Peppers
description: Hearty, wholesome and meatless!!! This veggie-friendly dinner doesn't skimp on satisfaction. Protein-packed Meatless Farm® patties, nourishing black beans and wholesome sweet potatoes make a tasty trio in every spoonful.
